citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:00 p.m. on 23 JAN
24.
Upon arriving at the facility I knocked on the front door and rang the door bell. I also called the contact number and left a
message. The licensee returned my call a few minutes later and stated that she was out of state and unavailable for
inspection.
End Section
